AutoCut Studio

This project is derived from AutoCut:
https://github.com/mli/autocut

AutoCut is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

This repository preserves the upstream AutoCut git history. AutoCut Studio
specific development begins after upstream commit:
ba2bb3bfbd57454727780eafad2861d66af58567

AutoCut Studio adds:
- A native SwiftUI macOS audio editing application.
- A JSON project model for podcast editing.
- A Python JSON backend for probing, waveform extraction, transcription,
  retranscription, and export.
- Preview playback behavior that skips unchecked transcript segments.
- Podcast-oriented padding behavior for silence cuts and exact behavior for
  manual speech cuts.

